Modelling a flushing toilet in Dymola using Modelica Fluids

The humble toilet accounts for the majoirty of a person's water consumption on a daily basis. It can be analysed easily using Modelica Fluids! Read the complete article [here]( https://www.claytex.com/blog/methods/modelling-a-flushing-toilet-in-dymola/)

